/i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F085230_93e62f84a0968453b9e71ac5577976db.png&h=2c776dc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"Sor 我撐佢呢個時候乜都唔好認<br />\n搞呢啲嘢一定要學老共 最緊要面皮厚呀<br />\n唔洗咁正直<br />\n<br />\n有必要去外國拎政治庇護"}]}